### Create Playlist

This endpoint allows the creation of a new playlist.

#### Request Body
- `name` (text): The name of the playlist.
- `description` (text): A brief description of the playlist.

#### Response
The response for this request follows the JSON schema below:

```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "playlistId": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  }
}
```

### POST /track

This endpoint is used to track a URL and associate it with a specific playlist.

#### Request Body

- `url` (text): The URL to be tracked.

- `playlist_id` (text): The ID of the playlist to which the URL will be associated.


#### Response

The response for this request follows the JSON schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  }
}

 ```
